column5:
@fasttrack
i agree. and i actually hope self-service buffets go away for good, including cruise ships. they've never been what i would consider, hygienic in anyway.
recently, on some of my trips i notice at least they push the sanitizer on folks standing in line, make them wear masks and even request the guests put on disposable gloves when entering the line. but, staff served food will always be more hygienic, not 100% but better than selfservice.
